CREATE TABLE `learn_record` ( `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `user` int(11) NOT NULL, `big_question` int(11) NOT NULL, `question` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0', `score` int(11) NOT NULL, `timestamp` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, PRIMARY KEY (`id`), UNIQUE KEY `idlog_UNIQUE` (`id`), KEY `test_idx` (`big_question`), KEY `foreign_tiny_idx` (`question`), KEY `user_idx` (`user`), CONSTRAINT `foreign_big` FOREIGN KEY (`big_question`) REFERENCES `big_question` (`id`) ON DELETE NO ACTION ON UPDATE NO ACTION, CONSTRAINT `foreign_tiny` FOREIGN KEY (`question`) REFERENCES `questions` (`id`) ON DELETE NO ACTION ON UPDATE NO ACTION, CONSTRAINT `user` FOREIGN KEY (`user`) REFERENCES `user` (`id`) ON DELETE NO ACTION ON UPDATE NO ACTION ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COMMENT='学习记录'
